test_name: MOMYOB should be the same as UDSv3
short_desc: UDSv4 MOMYOB should be equal to UDSv3 MOMYOB at the previous visit where MOMYOB is not blank
full_desc: UDSv4 Q1a1. MOMYOB (Mom birth year) should be equal to UDSv3 Q5a2. MOMYOB (Mom birth year) at the previous visit where UDSv3 MOMYOB is not blank
test_logic: If MOMYOB ne MOMYOB[UDSv3] at PREVVIS where MOMYOB is not blank

test_name: MOMDAGE should be the same as UDSv3
short_desc: UDSv4 MOMDAGE should be equal to UDSv3 MOMDAGE at the previous visit where MOMDAGE is not blank
full_desc: UDSv4 Q1a2. MOMDAGE (Mom death age) should be equal to UDSv3 Q5a3. MOMDAGE (Mom death age) at the previous visit where MOMDAGE is not blank
test_logic: If MOMDAGE ne MOMDAGE[UDSv3] at PREVVIS where MOMYOB[UDSv3] is not missing

test_name: MOMETPR should align with MOMNEUR in UDSv
short_desc: If UDSv3 MOMNEUR <8 at the previous visit where MOMNEUR is not blank, then UDSv4 MOMETPR should not equal 00
full_desc: If UDSv3 Q5a4. MOMNEUR (Mom neurological problem) <8 (Mom has a neurological problem or psychiatric condition) at the previous visit where MOMNEUR  is not blank, then UDSv4 Q1a3. MOMETPR (Mom primary dx) should not equal 00 (No known neurological/psychiatric diagnosis)
test_logic: If MOMNEUR[UDSv3] <8 at PREVVIS where MOMNEUR[UDSv3] is not blank and MOMETPR =00

test_name: DADYOB should be the same as UDSv3
short_desc: UDSv4 DADYOB should be equal to UDSv3 DADYOB at the previous visit where DADYOB is not blank
full_desc: UDSv4 Q1b1. DADYOB (Dad birth year) should be equal to UDSv3 Q5b2. DADYOB (Dad birth year) at the previous visit where UDSv3 DADYOB is not blank
test_logic: If DADYOB ne DADYOB[UDSv3,UDSv2] at PREVVIS where DADYOB is not blank

test_name: DADDAGE should be the same as UDSv3
short_desc: UDSv4 DADDAGE should be equal to UDSv3 DADDAGE at the previous visit where DADDAGE is not blank
full_desc: UDSv4 Q1b2. DADDAGE (Dad death age) should be equal to UDSv3 Q5b3. DADDAGE (Dad death age) at the previous visit where DADDAGE is not blank
test_logic: If DADDAGE ne DADDAGE[UDSv3] at PREVVIS where DADYOB[UDSv3] is not missing

test_name: DADETPR should align with DADNEUR in UDSv3
short_desc: If UDSv3 DADNEUR <8 at the previous visit where DADNEUR is not blank, then UDSv4 DADETPR should not equal 00
full_desc: If UDSv3 Q5a4. DADNEUR (DAD neurological problem) <8 (DAD has a neurological problem or psychiatric condition) at the previous visit where DADNEUR  is not blank, then UDSv4 Q1b3. DADETPR (DAD primary dx) should not equal 00 (No known neurological/psychiatric diagnosis)
test_logic: If DADNEUR[UDSv3] <8 at PREVVIS where DADNEUR[UDSv3] is not blank and DADETPR =00

test_name: SIBS should be the same as UDSv1-3
short_desc: UDSv4 SIBS should be equal to UDSv3 SIBS at the previous visit where SIBS is not blank
full_desc: UDSv4 Q2. SIBS (How many siblings?) should be equal to UDSv3 Q6. SIBS (How many siblings?) at the previous visit where SIBS is not blank
test_logic: If SIBS ne SIBS[UDSv3,UDSv2,UDSv1] at PREVVIS where SIBS[UDSv3,UDSv2,UDSv1] is not blank

test_name: KIDS should be the same as UDSv1-3
short_desc: UDSv4 KIDS should be equal to UDSv3 KIDS at the previous visit where KIDS is not blank
full_desc: UDSv4 Q3. KIDS (How many biological children?) should be equal to UDSv3 Q7. KIDS (How many biological children?) at the previous visit where KIDS is not blank
test_logic: If KIDS ne KIDS[UDSv3,UDSv2,UDSv1] at PREVVIS where KIDS[UDSv3,UDSv2,UDSv1] is not blank
